full_text: Julia Carolyn Margaret Morris  is an Australian comedian, actress, writer, television presenter and television producer who has worked extensively in Australian television and radio, touring the country with her solo comedy shows. She relocated to the United Kingdom in 2000, appearing on British television, then returned to Australia in 2007. She is also the narrator of the 2004 Australian chat show, Cherry Hall.
title: Julia Morris
